snippet: Rafael Nadal reached the final of the Qatar Open by coming from behind to beat a qualifier, Peter Gojowczyk, 4-6, 6-2, 6-3.
abstract: Rafael Nadal beats Peter Gojowczyk to reach men's final of the Qatar Open.
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal reached the final of the Qatar Open by coming from behind to beat a qualifier, Peter Gojowczyk, 4-6, 6-2, 6-3.

headline.main: Nadal Comes From Behind to Advance in Qatar
